Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.22,0:00:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 你在这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.83,0:00:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是罗兰德将校的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是从艾斯塔布尔村子里掳来的娈童？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳…琉特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大点声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫塔尔罗姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你我的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了没 莱纳·琉特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想活命就给我拼死干活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想通了就快动手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:00:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在那发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心我杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:42.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}眠り解きあぐねて　君を見失い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:42.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}漫长沉睡中醒来 却发现失去了你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:47.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}壊したくなる今すべて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:47.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}此刻恨不能破坏一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.93,0:01:56.36,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}望む言葉が二度と聞けないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.93,0:01:56.36,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}若再也听不到 那令人心动的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:02:02.61,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}命さえ無為に差し出すでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:02:02.61,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}我宁愿徒然付出生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:10.14,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}消えそうな輝きへと寄り添う想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:10.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}心绪飘向那若隐若现的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.59,0:02:16.86,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}孤独だよ　私の元にも朝日がくるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.59,0:02:16.86,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}一阵孤独 是否我亦能拥有明日朝阳？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:24.32,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}答えて…ふたりを繋ぐ愛があると
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:24.32,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}告诉我 我们之间还有爱相连
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.52,0:02:30.84,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}招かれた絶望の果てに立ち向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.52,0:02:30.84,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}让我能直面眼前那无尽绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:37.86,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}産まれて滅びる人の意識こそが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:37.86,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}正是生而即逝的人之意识
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:48.46,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}未来を選び　鍵を開ける
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:48.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}才能选择未来 打开那心锁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}奈尔法皇国 旅店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉丝跳跃冲拳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}忘却碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能不要每次一登场就打我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准你碰伊莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被禽兽碰过就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我一碰就会怀孕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.14,0:03:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是菲莉丝这么跟你说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的啦 放心放心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.04,0:03:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你抓着我妹妹的手是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拐骗幼女强奸怀孕什么的意思绝对没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近渐渐能从你那无表情中读出表情的我真是个天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了 伊莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路平安吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我好想姐姐一路飞奔过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉丝…很强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是哄可爱的妹妹睡觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:03:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这也叫哄人睡觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小时候兄长就是这么哄我睡觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的一家子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团子到底还是维尼特团子店的好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空吃东西还不来照顾下妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这能为她的将来负责吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}罗兰德城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉丝应该平安到达了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我的消息来得及送到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 这个好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从早到晚团子团子团子个没完
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉丝 你是来干嘛的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？嗯…这个 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉丝 拿了信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是席恩哥哥说要加急送来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是很重要的信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你快看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 呃…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的东西 不能丢的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 上哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩有没有跟你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 他说龙突然消失了什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那条莫名危险的龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要我们去调查其原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 呃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还说了什么很重要的话似的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正去了就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真麻…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然很想去查查看了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉丝 你去告诉席恩我们这就去查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于前几天 你们所报告的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面上长出龙的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,0:06:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说那森林周围的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已被赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件遗物就放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要再接近那森林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}奈尔法皇国 森林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这喝茶应该挺风雅的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如放弃调查什么的麻烦事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就来喝个茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成是那条龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去调查原因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有流血
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以虽然死了这么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却完全没有血腥味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那边两位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你们是奈尔法的秘密监察官二人组
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是来看传说中的龙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙能刺激作家的想象力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:08:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突如其来掳走了公主的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜错了别怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会搞出个勇者毅然反抗恶龙这种下三滥剧情来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以哥哥你的书永远都卖不出去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是丈二和尚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 尸体都没有流血
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事 请你们解释一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 果然被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们杀的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们潜入那堡垒的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.57,0:08:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和二位一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说能理解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也在找勇者遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才放任我们的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们找到遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:09:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 多亏破忌者部队的人们帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进展顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出所料你们找到了遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还弃之不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是感激不尽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们把看到龙的人全都杀掉灭口了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了避免得知遗物存在的人增加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要独占未知的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你们也要死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是什…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集勇者遗物有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你们以为自己可以活下去是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会问这种问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 其实这问题也是多余的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道你们是哪个国家派来的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾献上契约之文
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿沉眠于大地中恶意之精兽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提升身体能力的魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快好快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西 无 阵 向阳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.88,0:10:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西 无 阵 向阳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复写眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…之处孕育光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧 中途停止都能偷取吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 再怎么被我的美貌迷得神魂颠倒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不至于选这个时机来非礼我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么还这么从容不迫的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来都是很从容的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多从容？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你没来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就从容地死在刚才的攻击下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:10:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那镰刀很棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是勇者遗物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看来是能将持有者的身体能力提升到变态的镰刀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体不流一滴血
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及刚才的冰墙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是那镰刀的能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几次交锋之后 结冰的剑会变得越来越重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外加周围气温也会下降
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动会不够敏捷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用火焰魔法掩护你制造空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去搞定那镰刀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一试了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 作战方案敲定了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那敢情好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的复写眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是贵重的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要结晶化夺走才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结晶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你身为复写眼持有者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.68,0:11:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 比我还了解复写眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们似乎一无所知呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟他们连这“忘却碎片”都随手扔掉了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“忘却碎片”？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就展示一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们所丢弃的遗物的使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是遗物的使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“多尔艾利之剑鳞”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以根据使用者的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:13:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将攻击对象燃烧殆尽的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 地面是没有意志的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以从地面长出来时是完全无害的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 可以开始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们好好尝尝遗物的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有闲工夫作壁上观啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求雷鸣 电光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是勇者遗物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 库的“艾尔克罗诺之镰”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“朵尔艾利之剑鳞”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及这“爱蕾米奥之簪”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕴藏着可将魔法无效化的神力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三件遗物…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去没胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共鸣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 莱纳 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望一切都消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们对莱纳做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不使其觉醒 就无法夺取复写眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉醒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复写眼被人厌恶忌讳的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为会失控破坏一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以人称疯狂的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不祥的杀戮者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在即是麻烦的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝…快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离我…远点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的…我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变成怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人会死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这一切都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 结束这一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随心所欲地释放一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放 杀戮 所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认持有者崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们对莱纳做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是恶魔失控 即将大肆破坏而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会杀了他夺取结晶的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.43,0:16:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你也看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那点力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将在这“爱蕾米奥之簪”的神力下化为乌有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解析存在 解除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 蝼蚁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯伊哥 还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是普通的复写眼持有者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要杀吾？用那点力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区爱蕾米奥就想杀了吾？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匍匐在地的蝼蚁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:17:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 消失吧消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:17:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切皆为无
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回归无吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 库
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是什么复写眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论逃往何方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切终将归于无
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起源（α）即是破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾不行创造
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行惠泽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅行消除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回归纯白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不寂寞吗 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会 有大家在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:19:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来当莱纳的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后要叫我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我来当爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.23,0:19:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟德尔做夫妇 才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肮脏的盗尸贼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把偷走的东西叫出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 我们会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放过我女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了克伊尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求烧原 红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼 你们敢反抗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求烧原 红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子 那眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克伊尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是复写眼持有者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克伊尔？
